		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+16" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Dear Aunt Wendy and Uncle Graham,</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">I don't know if mum told you but I've got a new job! I'm working for World Aid, a <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[1]</FONT> that provides <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[2]</FONT> for developing countries. I haven't joined as a <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[3]</FONT> though – I'm getting paid! My job is to <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[4]</FONT> for specific projects in various parts of the world so I have to <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[5]</FONT> of the different causes that need help to try and get <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[6]</FONT> of money.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Basically, I have to organise as many <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[7]</FONT> as possible. I've got lots of ideas like pop concerts and art exhibitions, but I'm going to start small with a sponsored walk from Hinkton to Fiston on the first Sunday in May. I know you two are really busy but I was wondering if I could enlist your help a little? I haven't had much luck with my friends, I'm afraid – it's not that they're not <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[8]</FONT>, it's just that they're all too poor and too busy to help out at the moment.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">What I need first of all are walkers – and I know you have lots of friends who like walking – so I was wondering if you could ask them if they'd like to take part and get <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[9]</FONT> to pay for each mile they walk. It really is for a <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[10]</FONT>. All the <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[11]</FONT> will go towards food for the victims of the Zimba floods, who are dying of starvation. You must have seen the awful footage on television and some of the <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[12]</FONT> that they've been making for people to help.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Anyway, if you really can't help, I do understand, but if there's any way you can <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[13]</FONT>, I'd really appreciate it.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">I'm afraid I have to dash as I have to write to a few more people!</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
